# ============================================================
# AGENT COMMUNICATION PROTOCOL
# ============================================================

When starting a task:
1. Claim the task by logging: "AGENT_NAME claiming TASK_X"
2. Check dependencies are complete
3. Read config.py
4. Write code
5. Test with sample data
6. Mark task complete: "AGENT_NAME completed TASK_X"

When blocked:
1. Log: "AGENT_NAME blocked on TASK_X, waiting for TASK_Y"
2. Move to another task if possible

When sharing artifacts:
1. Log: "AGENT_NAME created ARTIFACT_NAME at PATH"
2. Validate artifact before marking complete

